data.description: This beautiful 2 story, 4 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath home is secluded on a double cul-de-sac street with no thru traffic and it backs to a greenbelt. This "almost new" 3 year old home is walking distance to the splash pad, pool & park. The owners hand picked this lot due to its pool sized back yard, which comes with a covered patio and sprinkler system. This versatile plan offers a flex room in the front of the home and an open living space in the rear of the home. The kitchen boasts granite counters, an island with a breakfast bar, and stainless appliances.  The primary suite is on the first floor and includes, double sinks, shower and garden tub. There are 3 additional bedrooms, a bathroom and a large game room on the second floor. Zoned to HIGHLY ACCLAIMED LCISD schools including Frost Elementary and Foster High School. Minutes from Grand Parkway & Westpark Toll Road where you will find plenty of shopping, dining and entertainment options.  Why pay new construction prices?  Schedule soon!!
